{"title":"常用CSS","uid":"d471cbb5d3a5e8775b58ce1c8d851097","slug":"frontend/css","date":"2023-09-14T03:15:44.609Z","updated":"2024-03-06T06:35:36.720Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/frontend/css.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2023/09/14/SqB2imZdaP7gMWX.png","content":"<p>本文主要记录一些常用css，经常用但是还是记不住，每次都要上网搜好麻烦啊所以特此开了本文。本文包括文字，图片，背景，动画，定位，布局，滚动条等样式，以及一些样式属性的介绍。</p>\n<h3 id=\"文本篇\"><a href=\"#文本篇\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文本篇\"></a>文本篇</h3><h4 id=\"文本省略号\"><a href=\"#文本省略号\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文本省略号\"></a>文本省略号</h4><div class=\"language-css\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">css</span><pre class=\"shiki nord\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">.</span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">text</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">overflow</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">hidden;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">text-overflow</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">ellipsis;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">white-space</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">nowrap;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><h5 id=\"placeholder-省略号\"><a href=\"#placeholder-省略号\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"placeholder 省略号\"></a><code>placeholder</code> 省略号</h5><div class=\"language-css\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">css</span><pre class=\"shiki nord\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">input</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">:</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">placeholder-shown</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">text-overflow</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">ellipsis;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">// or</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">input</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">[</span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">placeholder</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">]</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">text-overflow</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">ellipsis;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><h4 id=\"文本下划线距离\"><a href=\"#文本下划线距离\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文本下划线距离\"></a>文本下划线距离</h4><div class=\"language-css\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">css</span><pre class=\"shiki nord\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">.</span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">text</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">text-underline-offset</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">1</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">rem;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"图片\"><a href=\"#图片\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"图片\"></a>图片</h3><div class=\"language-css\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">css</span><pre class=\"shiki nord\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">img</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">,</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">video</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    // 设置内容适应到其使用高度和宽度确定的框的方式</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    // </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">contain</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">内容将被缩放，保持填充元素在内容框内保持其宽高比。当内容的宽高比和框的宽高比不匹配将被添加黑边</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">    // </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">cover</span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">: 内容保持宽高比并填充元素的整个内容框，如果宽高比不一致则剪裁以适应内容框</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">    // </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">fill</span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">: 内容正好填充元素的内容框，整个对象将完全填充此框，如果宽高比不一致则拉伸以适应内容框</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">    // </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">none</span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">: 保持原有尺寸</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">    object-fit: </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">cover;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">object-position</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">50</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">%</span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\"> </span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">50</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">%;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">div</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">background-image</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">url</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">()</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    // </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">contain</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">在容器内尽可能大地缩放图像，而不裁剪或拉伸图像。如果容器大于图像，这将导致图像平铺，除非将background-repeat 属性设置为no-repeat。</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">    // </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">cover</span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">: 将图像（同时保留其比例）缩放到尽可能小的尺寸以填充容器（即：其高度和宽度完全覆盖容器），不留任何空白空间。如果背景的比例与元素不同，则图像将被垂直或水平裁剪。</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">    background-size: </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">cover;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"媒体查询篇\"><a href=\"#媒体查询篇\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"媒体查询篇\"></a>媒体查询篇</h3><h4 id=\"打印\"><a href=\"#打印\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"打印\"></a>打印</h4><div class=\"language-scss\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">scss</span><pre class=\"shiki nord\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D08770\">@media</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">print</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">.</span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">print-content</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #616E88\">// 打印背景图片</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">-webkit-print-color-adjust</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">exact;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">.</span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">print-item</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #616E88\">// 防止元素被截断</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">page-break-inside</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">avoid;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"布局篇\"><a href=\"#布局篇\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"布局篇\"></a>布局篇</h3><h4 id=\"flex-布局\"><a href=\"#flex-布局\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"flex 布局\"></a>flex 布局</h4><div class=\"language-css\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">css</span><pre class=\"shiki nord\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">.</span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">flex</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">display</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">flex;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    // </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">flex</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> 方向：row =&gt; 水平；</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">column</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">：垂直；</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">flex-direction</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">row;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    // 和 </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">flex</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> 方向垂直方向居中。</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    aligin-items</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">center;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    // 和 </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">flex</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> 方向相同方向居中</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">justify-content</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">center;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    // 每个元素之间的间距 8 个像素</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">gap</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">8</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">px;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">.</span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">flex-item</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    // </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">flex</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> 代表三个属性：</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">flex-grow</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">flex-shrink</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">flex-basis</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    // 默认值，相当于 </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">flex</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">：1 1 auto</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">flex</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">auto;</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">    // </span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9\">flex</span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">:</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">1</span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\"> =&gt; </span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">flex</span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">: </span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">1</span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\"> </span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">1</span><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\"> </span><span style=\"color: #B48EAD\">0</span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">%</span></